title: El Kabeer
overview: The mayor of Al-Mazareeta, a small town in upper Egypt, met an American woman and had twins with her. One child stayed in Al-Mazareeta while the other went to America with his mother. After the mayor's death, the child that grew up in America goes over to Egypt to claim his father's title. The sons battle to see who will take over, but eventually they realize the value of family and go through challenges together.
